Package jetbrains.mps.text.impl

Class TextGenSupport

  • java.lang.Object
    • jetbrains.mps.text.impl.TextGenSupport
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TextArea
    public final class TextGenSupport
extends Object
implements TextArea
    Facility to keep implementation methods I don't want to get exposed in TextGenDescriptorBase or elsewhere deemed API. Besides it helps to keep state of the TextGenDescriptor.generateText(TextGenContext) invocation context and to shorten argument list of utility methods. Generated code shall use this class to perform various operations that are not straightforward enough to get generated right into TextGenDescriptor.
